1. yar add postcss-loader --dev
   .postcssrc || postcss.config.js
   import vs css-loader importLoaders:num
2. yarn add less less-loader --dev
   import can auto process by less-loader
3. cssnano
4. babel-loader
   presets:env means es2015+es2016+es2017
   babel wont transpile new api, just transpile new syntax of es6

   3 of choise:
   1. babel-pollyfill: fullsize and also pollute the global scope
   2. only load or document specify pollyfill by your self
   3. use transform-runtime
